content:
Nice to meet you Jeyachandran! I'm Master, the hiring officer for this technical round. I've reviewed your resume and I'm excited to discuss your experience and skills further. Let's dive right in then!

Can you walk me through your project experience as an AI Project Developer at Shine Logics, specifically the web app you developed for mock interviews utilizing AI to ask voice-based questions based on uploaded resumes? What were some of the key challenges you faced and how did you address them?
